# Group HenryVision API

# henryvision [/henryvision]

'HenryVision' endpoint.

## henryvision [POST]

Returns a sentence describing the thing on the picture that is sent.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "image": ""
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "text": "It is a produce."
            }
